/**
 * Wave 10 W10-5A: embedded Apple PassKit template assets.
 *
 * Apple PassKit (.pkpass) bundles need icon + logo PNGs at
 * specific @1x / @2x / @3x densities. We embed them as base64
 * strings here so the serverless function can build a pass
 * without filesystem access. Total embedded weight: ~13KB.
 *
 * To regenerate (e.g. on a brand update), re-run
 * scripts/gen-wallet-assets.mjs (or the inline node script in W10-5A PR).
 */
